  "abilities": {
    "core": [
      "Deadly Demise D3 FACTION: Nurgle\u2019s Gift (Aura) Death Guard Defenders: While this model is within 3\" of one or more friendly DEATH GUARD INFANTRY units, this model has the Lone Operative ability. Fevered Strategist: Once per battle round , one model from your army with this ability can use it when a friendly DEATH GUARD unit within 12\" of that model is targeted with a Stratagem. If it does, reduce the CP cost of that usage of that Stratagem by 1CP. Miasma of Pestilence (Aura): While a friendly DEATH GUARD unit is within 6\" of this model, each time a ranged attack targets that unit, models in that unit have the Benefit of Cover against that attack."
    ],
